  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个三层权限架构的流程图，用来展示不同信任级别下的数据处理流程。最外层是Public层，中间是Private，最内层是Trusted。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "T2",
        "T3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三层嵌套结构。每层都是一个subgraph对吧？我先确认一下命名：第一层叫Tier 1: Public，第二层Tier 2: Private，第三层Tier 3: Trusted？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "T2",
        "T3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就这三个层级。Tier 1处理公开工具数据，入口是Tool JSON，输出Artifact。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "T1In",
        "T1Out"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Tier 1画好了，包含Tool JSON到Artifact的流转。现在Tier 2的Private层需要什么样的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "T2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Tier 2要复杂一点，入口是File Stats，中间要加一个Gate做审批判断，最后输出Comment。这个Gate是菱形决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T2",
        "T2In",
        "T2Gate",
        "T2Out"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Gate用菱形表示。Tier 2的结构是File Stats → Gate → Comment。接下来Tier 3呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T2In",
        "T2Gate",
        "T2Out"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Tier 3是最高信任区，入口Code Diff，中间有个Defense模块做安全检测，最后输出Artifact。注意这里Defense是矩形处理节点，不是菱形。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T3",
        "T3In",
        "T3Def",
        "T3Out"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三层结构都画好了。现在需要把层级之间的关系连起来，T1到T2到T3的递进关系怎么体现？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "T2",
        "T3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用简洁的连线，T1指向T2，T2指向T3，表示数据或权限的流转方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "T2",
        "T3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "层级关系线加好了。现在需要定义样式class，让不同节点有视觉区分。您希望用什么配色方案？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef",
        "class"
